title: 12/17/12 DPS Hour 3
itunes:title: 12/17/12 DPS Hour 3
description:
Dan talks about the possibility of NFL games being postponed due to the Covid virus. Dan tries to understand how the virus can effect tie breakers as games proceed with out key players for teams.
